How do you get idParent? I just gonna match emails instead.


2. Display parents infomation

SELECT *
FROM Parents
WHERE Parents.idParent = 'Parents.idParent?';

2. Display parent kids

SELECT Students.idStudent
FROM Students, Parents
WHERE Students.idParent1 = 'Parents.idParent' OR Students.idParent2 = 'Parents.idParent'

2. Display all messages associate with parents

SELECT idMessage
FROM Messages
WHERE Messages.idSender = 'idParent' or Messages.idRecipient = 'idParent';

3. Allow Parents Change infomation

UPDATE email, uname, pass
FROM Parents
WHERE Parents.idParent = 'idParent?';
